<plot>Which do you follow? Your heart of your head? It's 1964 and even small town Indiana is feeling the tension of the Civil Rights Movement. Teenagers Rosalie, black, and Jesse, white, are in love. They take extreme measures to make sure their relationship remains a secret. Their dream is to get out of their small town and live a better life. When Jesse's father discovers them, it sets off a chain of events that rips their plans apart and ultimately forces Rosalie to make the hardest decision of her life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?008341</url></doc>
